You need to  keep up to date  and  decide what actions you will take  if the situation changes.    Currently as at 9.40am Friday 5 February a bushfire is travelling in a westerly direction in the vicinity of Sunshine Acres.    People in the area will be affected by smoke, which will reduce visibility and air quality.Â   Properties are not under direct threat at this time.
